Which one should you use?
Use cURL if you are writing a script that needs to run on someone else's machine or a server.

Use HTTPie if you are testing an API manually and want the most "friendly" experience possible.

Use Curlie if you want that "pretty" look but find yourself missing the speed and raw power of cURL's flags.

